# Roadmap — Symbion Space

## v0.1 — Foundational (Q4 2025)
- PSL v0.1 (RC): grammar, sections, minimal linter rules
- GeoBench pilot suite: Meal Planner (CSR/HRR/EBR/PCT)
- Docs: contribution, code of conduct, repo layout

## v0.2 — Orchestration (Q1 2026)
- Reference “Syndicate” roles: generator/auditor/optimizer/verifier
- Pluggable graders + CI hooks (pre-merge PSL checks)
- Minimal datasets for 2 more domains (planning, compliance)

## v0.3 — Scale & Trust (Q2 2026)
- Multi-domain GeoBench with baseline reports
- Evidence binding format `[SRC:#]` and traceable outputs
- Confidence fields in PSL: `[CONFIDENCE score=…]`

## v0.4 — Autonomy & Memory (Q3 2026)
- Agent loops `[LOOP max=N]`, rollback contracts
- Session memory & long-horizon tasks (days/weeks)
- Public benchmarks & leaderboards

> Principle: not more parameters — better orchestration and verifiability.
